{"tid":1370862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.27「勇武」記得買飛撘地鐵","createTime":"2019-07-27T06:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:53:18.000Z","uid":140288,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c917e75d449607bb8610f807e654d956d14d546","tid":1370862,"uid":140288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOzvAW5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOzvAW5.png&h=1ce402c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a13a9df8dfc8a774ff588babf761a729b2122b0","tid":1370862,"uid":61520,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"雖然好多POST有講 而且都有前線手足出POST講左唔會入村<br />\n但都要再次提醒巴絲<br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不主動攻擊 不入村 受攻擊就即時還擊 執行公民拘捕令 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去食老婆餅的巴絲帶多幾條索帶去包手信 餅盒太多條繩會頂唔順斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]記者開遮"},{"pid":"fa2bac639977dabbe5d06cfe0296d557da8bc6de","tid":1370862,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f953827587db6dac8662bd5ef22aecf3707ca8e6","tid":1370862,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5f9fb1d097ebc8825835bef7743152e85fe2ae","tid":1370862,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"人人自備口哨、長遮"},{"pid":"5c4e404d8b0d616ac27da28fee8f41077a4eff67","tid":1370862,"uid":140288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"朗屏14:50<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1UvA7p.png\" data-thumbnail-